---
By: Ramana Maharshi
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 116
    Verse: 5
Tags:
  - Ego/Vanity
---
The more you prune a plant, the more it grows. So too the more you seek to
annihilate the ego, the more it will increase. You should seek the root of
the ego and destroy it.
